# Speech-to-Text Setup

Simple Speech-to-Text using OpenAI Whisper

## Quick Start

```bash
# Record and transcribe
bash record_audio.sh

# Or just transcribe existing file
python3 stt.py recording.wav
```

## Files

- `stt.py` - Main transcription script
- `record_audio.sh` - Record audio and transcribe
- `stt/README.md` - Documentation
